OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1779948269
OL,3,CLondon Ambulance Services sees busiest
OL,4,Cday since the pandemic
OL,6,FThe London Ambulance Service
OL,7,Fexperienced its busiest day since the
OL,8,FCovid pandemic after temperatures
OL,9,Fpassed 35 Celsius.
OL,11,FThe 999 control room received over
OL,12,F8,000 calls with a record number of
OL,13,Fcalls from 2pm until midnight.
OL,15,FPeople are being urged to call 999 in
OL,16,Fa life-threatening emergency only and
OL,17,Fconsider using a GP and NHS 111 or NHS
OL,18,F111 online.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
